Title: MY IMS Website Template
Description:
MY IMS Website Template is an ASP.NET pre-designed website, all you need to do is add your own personal content/ logo and you're ready to jump start your own website.
It has good structure and uses: Web User Controls for header & footer, Sitemap for the menus, Master page etc.
